  <!-- EN: giant spider -->
  <VAECaves_GiantSpider.label>毒噬巨蛛</VAECaves_GiantSpider.label>
  <!-- EN: A type of arthropod, Giant Spiders are in fact nowhere near the size of the common house spiders humans are used to. However, similar rules apply - they lay eggs in spider lairs, sting their prey with venomous stinger and wrap it in cocoons for when the time is right to feast. They regenerate their wounds fast and are very susceptible to fire.\n\nThe mature giant spider is the most commonly met life stage of a giant spider. Their powerful fang bite will stun their prey for a very long period of time, giving the giant spider enough time to wrap it in the spidersilk cocoon.\n\nSpecial mechanics: If attacked, all other giant spiders nearby, in any life stage, will enrage and assault the colony. -->
  <VAECaves_GiantSpider.description>一种节肢动物，毒噬巨蛛实际上远不及人类所常见的普通家养蜘蛛的大小。然而，它们的习性却非常相似————在蜘蛛巢穴中产卵，用毒刺捕猎，然后用茧包裹起来，以备不时之需。它们的伤口再生速度很快，但非常容易着火。\n\n毒噬巨蛛成年体是毒噬巨蛛中最常见的成长阶段。它们强大的尖牙会在很长一段时间内使猎物昏迷，让毒噬巨蛛有足够的时间将其包裹在蛛丝茧中。\n\n特殊机制：如果受到攻击，附近的所有毒噬巨蛛，无论处于任何成长阶段，都会被激怒并攻击殖民地。它们的近战攻击会引起感染。</VAECaves_GiantSpider.description>
